title: `$file::size()`
description: Convert file size.
...

~~~ .php.xmp
File::size($file, $unit = null, $prec = 2);
~~~

**Options:** `B`, `KB`, `MB`, `GB`, `TB`

~~~ .php
echo File::size('path\to\file.txt'); // automatic (as short as possible)
~~~

~~~ .php
echo File::size('path\to\file.txt', 'KB'); // force to `KB`
~~~

~~~ .php
